         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Public Library ¶ 3rd August 1869 ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I do myself the honor to inform you that the Trustees of the M. P. ¶ Melbourne Public. ¶  ¶ Library are now able to receive in the Great Hall of the Museum...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">69.08.03</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Redmond Barry</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">4366/PO/3, pp. 407-8 outward letter books of registered correspondence, VA912 Trustees of the Public Library, Museums and National Gallery, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Public Library</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">3rd August 1869</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I do myself the honor to inform you that the Trustees of the M. P.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Melbourne Public.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Library are now able to receive in the Great Hall of the Museum, objects illustrating the Natural History and industrial resources of Victoria. —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>2, The Minister of Mines has already contributed a very choice and extensive collection of Minerals, and the Trustees have placed these in position. —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>3, It will be very gratifying to the Trustees if you will afford them an opportunity of displaying types of such of the varied and highly interesting illustrations of Phytological Science as you can furnish from your department. —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>4, Specimens of the fibres, [timber],<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>barks, resins, tars, gums, oils essences, alkalis &amp;c &amp;c extracted from the woods of the country, with the results of the Chemical researches relating to the Botanical Kingdom which have been conducted under your direction, would be of especial value to inform the public of the processes recognised by you as most effectual as well as of the quality and commercial value of these and Similar products. —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>5, The Trustees will have particular pleasure in being thus instrumental in presenting to the public, through your<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>assistance, such a large fund of most important instruction, and at the same time allowing<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>visitors to the Museum to form a more just conception than they can at present of the practically useful original investigations<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>which you have so patiently pursued with such distinguished success.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The gist of each point is summarized in a note in the margin.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient Servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>(Signed) Redmond Barry</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>One of the Trustees of the M. P. Library</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr F. Müeller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Government Botanist</p>
         </div>
